rows.label: qst200825_msg0001
rows.name: Hi Chepaan, we brought the ingredients!

rows.label: qst200825_msg0003
rows.name:
I'll get mixing now.
Please bear with me a moment...

rows.label: qst200825_msg0004
rows.name:
Sorry for keeping you waiting, 
Hotaru-chan.

rows.label: qst200825_msg0005
rows.name:
Here are your Fungicide and
Antidesiccant.

rows.label: qst200825_msg0006
rows.name:
As for the tree brace, I would suggest
the Saets Lumber Company.

rows.label: qst200825_msg0007
rows.name:
Thank you for everything, Chepaan.
Really, we're in your debt.

rows.label: qst200825_msg0008
rows.name:
Don't mention it, child. It's enough
to see Hotaru-chan's radiant smile.

rows.label: qst200825_msg0013
rows.name:
Okay, let's head over to the
lumber company camp!

rows.label: qst200825_msg0014
rows.name:
Well, take care out there!
And do come to visit, hear?
